        {
            "id": 6010907,
            "title": "小米發表Redmi Pad 2平板新品 搭載聯發科8核心6奈米製程晶片 搶攻入門級娛樂",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>小米今 (6) 日發表全新 Redmi Pad 2 平板電腦，搭載聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)MediaTek Helio G100-Ultra 8 核心處理器，採用 6 奈米製程技術，帶來優異運算效能與能耗表現，</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010907%2Fl%2F1ef48303b97f98e45ca307b3474d52ef.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">小米發表Redmi Pad 2平板新品 搭載聯發科8核心6奈米製程晶片 搶攻入門級娛樂。(圖：小米提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>處理器規格成為新品核心亮點，MediaTek Helio G100-Ultra 採用先進 6 奈米工藝製程，8 核心架構設計提供穩定流暢的效能體驗。無論開啟多個應用程式、線上瀏覽或觀賞高畫質影片，皆能保持流暢不卡頓的操作感受，並配合 9000mAh 超大電池容量，實現全天候長效續航表現。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>螢幕規格方面，新品搭載 11.1 吋 2560x1600 解析度螢幕，支援 90Hz 更新率與 16 比 10 顯示比例。聯發科晶片強大的圖形處理能力，確保滑動、切換與動畫呈現更為流暢順暢，提升日常操作體驗。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>音效系統配備立體聲四揚聲器設計，支援 Dolby Atmos 與 Hi-Res Audio 高解析音質。聯發科處理器的多媒體處理能力，配合專業音效技術，提供劇院級的沉浸式音感體驗。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>產品搭載 Xiaomi HyperOS 2 系統，充分發揮聯發科晶片的運算能力，支援分割畫面與多工效率功能。系統介面操作直覺，大幅提升日常使用的便利性與實用價值。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>產品同步推出 Redmi Pad 2 4G 版本，處理器同樣採用 MediaTek Helio G100-Ultra 晶片。4G 版本額外支援雙卡雙 4G 通話與 GPS 導航功能，機身輕巧好攜帶，滿足各種行動需求。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
